{"tid":772133,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得令你開始影相既原因","createTime":"2018-08-08T13:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T05:54:55.000Z","uid":110463,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"dea0f6727ea43c32d6034f62d4f5c2351cbb8ebc","tid":772133,"uid":110463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:31:17.000Z","msg":"以前畢業個個都會拎部相機返學校影相<br />\n眼見十個有九個都有一部數碼相機<br />\n自己都心痕想有一部屬於自己既機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係無錢買數碼<br />\n最後買左部連測光都無嘅菲林機<br />\n<br />\n依加諗返只係因為人有我都要有既心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係咩都要由0開始學<br />\n我諗都係會得三分鐘熱度<br />\n<br />\n你又記唔記得咩原因你會開始你既影相之路？"},{"pid":"11f8c72720f2bcf3b42a8ff1adfba6e589478e10","tid":772133,"uid":50502,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"去grad trip 買左第一部相機 <br />\n<br />\n之後返工見同事玩相機 被毒後就入坑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bb3ad90b0ca832278ab7511e9c2c988b59d99b","tid":772133,"uid":18465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"數碼機起步冇耐果時貪得意買黎學影相<br />\n之後轉玩菲林，從此就踩左落個氹"},{"pid":"c7a0e23d59a695a77eef71380114e27db2727607","tid":772133,"uid":51747,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:28:51.000Z","msg":"2000年月全食<br />\n<br />\n叫亞爸教我用佢部FM2<br />\n然後就一條友出咗文化中心通頂影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0cd7031772a3b501ffd3411ee7df58de17eb3b","tid":772133,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"散景"},{"pid":"172dbe67a840d83b6d073813dbb683c61cc8fd16","tid":772133,"uid":143241,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:08:43.000Z","msg":"好細個已經想買部相機學攝影,但當年冇錢.依家出嚟做咗幾年嘢,儲咗啲錢.決定聽日放工就買部nikon玩下"},{"pid":"f3e2cbb23912ae7de24b832f739ef4f834c33cc4","tid":772133,"uid":150807,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"為左中學last day留念"},{"pid":"eee630899719dd7e385d7e69eddc811adf7d0300","tid":772133,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:16:26.000Z","msg":"貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f93c40e0bc442a942365966097390c1e190689","tid":772133,"uid":163791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"出左糧想買野 咁岩個期就買左部數碼相機"},{"pid":"5da1fd28a742da03422f69088a6173a78715dec0","tid":772133,"uid":56199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"男朋友"},{"pid":"adc02b38dc7619bf311f97343f917bad355e1f1e","tid":772133,"uid":32968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:00:12.000Z","msg":"有次細個去camp 帶左部數碼相機去周圍影相同拍片<br />\n返屋企睇相 覺得幾搞笑 <br />\n之後就開始成日周圍影"},{"pid":"69c5feac9c5370e5c42406d7b6910586faca57e1","tid":772133,"uid":3656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"返工有一項工作要影相做紀錄<br />\n自己on99買咗部數碼相機用<br />\n跟住覺得齋用嚟做嘢做紀錄好嘥<br />\n於是開始上網自學攝影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8022f4aa9db0b02627e89a35c93867dc93b154a","tid":772133,"uid":149200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"女朋友"},{"pid":"3eec1c055665ef163e95b059f3b559f014d7b659","tid":772133,"uid":828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"拍下過 記住過 好過擁有"},{"pid":"ec65c09f49b60ab6cf58aa8d28f7275e1c44b496","tid":772133,"uid":58931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"因為有野想影？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6dae726877160bffd1ed925368c85352b06487c","tid":772133,"uid":28741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"細細個屋企有部菲林機<br />\n自始就好想有自己既相機<br />\n因為相機創造回憶<br />\n到大有閒錢  就慢慢地鐘意自己去影相"},{"pid":"7ea9d67e2eaf0b98dcf87a5be721f42fbc7b93a5","tid":772133,"uid":8783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"我買相機影相既原因係影女朋友<br />\n但當我買完，就散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c8aa26662a734dbb89b3bb29ff9bb39e648234","tid":772133,"uid":13342,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"女朋友"},{"pid":"5ba0641c8f7f4d70b8c2aa9723ea6d9d4ec14d6b","tid":772133,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ea9d67e2eaf0b98dcf87a5be721f42fbc7b93a5","tid":772133,"uid":8783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"我買相機影相既原因係影女朋友<br />\n但當我買完，就散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"要積極 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f57859438933c184e35ae519fbed1dec0ce20a8","tid":772133,"uid":18465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5ba0641c8f7f4d70b8c2aa9723ea6d9d4ec14d6b","tid":772133,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ea9d67e2eaf0b98dcf87a5be721f42fbc7b93a5","tid":772133,"uid":8783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"我買相機影相既原因係影女朋友<br />\n但當我買完，就散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"要積極 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"積極咁買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb5a60453de9aad15b60b1d271f5b4fc23e92d2","tid":772133,"uid":8783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f57859438933c184e35ae519fbed1dec0ce20a8","tid":772133,"uid":18465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5ba0641c8f7f4d70b8c2aa9723ea6d9d4ec14d6b","tid":772133,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ea9d67e2eaf0b98dcf87a5be721f42fbc7b93a5","tid":772133,"uid":8783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"我買相機影相既原因係影女朋友<br />\n但當我買完，就散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"要積極 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"積極咁買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:46:18.000Z","msg":"不了，無底深潭<br />\n玩緊fujifilm 無反，幾支鏡夠玩<br />\n2 支定焦，2支變焦"},{"pid":"8dc8b4898f95a57f654a1fe455957394f0b502c2","tid":772133,"uid":38218,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"唔知大家幾年前有無係Youtube 睇過<br />\n一個叫 mockmoon2000 的 timelapse 片?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2lsXjltXhXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2lsXjltXhXg&d=O%2B%2FmjTQdNMYEhUtediYwEgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6b090ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2lsXjltXhXg</a><br />\n中學個時好迷佢夜空嘅timelapse<br />\n就係個時就好想影類似嘅相<br />\n但係無錢買  一直放係個心度<br />\n<br />\n然後<br />\n我樓下有條好長嘅行人路<br />\n兩旁種咗高大嘅樹<br />\n每逢三、四月期間<br />\n會重新生返d嫩葉<br />\n但好奇怪<br />\n個d初生嘅嫩葉都會係其中一兩日內<br />\n突然好似落雨咁不斷落葉 <br />\n個moment 好靚  <br />\n所以好想影個timelapse<br />\n<br />\n後來<br />\n上莊住hell 少咗時間返屋企<br />\n開始好掛住居住嘅地方<br />\n再加上自己住條村嘅街市被領展封殺<br />\n改建冷氣商場<br />\n一直都好想係佢接埋之前影返輯相<br />\n但係學校嘅事太忙  又無實行到<br />\n有日返到屋企  先驟覺已經圍板拆卸中<br />\n依家只可以睇返中三時 <br />\nArts堂其中一份功課的照片懷舊下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h69ddRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh69ddRQ.jpg&h=f6b69be8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RNAEIWK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRNAEIWK.jpg&h=17bbedff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mwe8g3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMwe8g3u.jpg&h=49acdf55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩年前入咗部死黑Fujil<br />\n不過夜空timelapse仲未學影<br />\n樓下行人路兩旁嘅樹又仲未影<br />\n新入相機個時轉影街拍<br />\n去到最近幾個月  星期一到五都做野做到好勞累<br />\n週未都係屋企  無再有心力出去掃街<br />\n<br />\n樓主問起  先醒返下最初做乜想買部相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3627d2f0ee072f3a823da89701457d90165311a","tid":772133,"uid":69792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T18:18:45.000Z","msg":"讀書嗰陣老豆買咗部700D比我，但嗰陣冇乜興趣<br />\n都係用嚟做下功課就算<br />\n後尾就嚟畢業屎忽痕買咗支wide angle就開始影風景<br />\n影影下轉返Nikon（成個家族都用Nikon）<br />\n到而家做埋影相佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d598f15819e529f6d787e9c13f8ee4020b3169","tid":772133,"uid":110463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11f8c72720f2bcf3b42a8ff1adfba6e589478e10","tid":772133,"uid":50502,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"去grad trip 買左第一部相機 <br />\n<br />\n之後返工見同事玩相機 被毒後就入坑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:21:13.000Z","msg":"同事功不可沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb4b4f55998ded302a0c107884d634482cc91e2","tid":772133,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:22:12.000Z","msg":"自得其樂，童年陰影"},{"pid":"a588a158f649cfae002af619b2ba1fb849259d5c","tid":772133,"uid":110463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a0e23d59a695a77eef71380114e27db2727607","tid":772133,"uid":51747,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:28:51.000Z","msg":"2000年月全食<br />\n<br />\n叫亞爸教我用佢部FM2<br />\n然後就一條友出咗文化中心通頂影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:26:47.000Z","msg":"一個人通頂影月亮？<br />\n作為開始都幾深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2429